<p>But first, create a <code>private function getService()</code> with an <code>$id</code> argument.
Woops - make that <code>protected</code> - the whole point of this method is to let
our test classes fetch services from the container. To do that, return
<code>self::$kernel-&gt;getContainer()-&gt;get($id)</code>:</p>
