</p>
<p>This should clear the <code>ObjectOrienter</code> out of the database and hopefully
get things passing. Try the test!</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">php bin/phpunit -c app src/AppBundle/Tests/Controller/API/ProgrammerControllerTest.php</div></code></pre>
<p>Drumroll! Oh no - still a 500 error. And we still can't see the error. Time
to take our debugging tools up a level.</p>

    
